Privacy Policy — La Citadelle – Vote Compagnon

Last updated: December 07, 2025

This application does not collect, store, or share any personal data.

1. Data Collection

The app does not collect any personal information, such as:

username or Minecraft nickname

email address

IP address

device identifiers

location

analytics or tracking data

No account creation is required.

2. Local Storage

The application only stores local preferences, such as:

vote cooldown timers

notification settings

Elytreum orb values

Rankup checklist progress

These values remain entirely on the user’s device and are never transmitted to any server.

3. External Websites

The app provides access to third-party voting websites through a browser tab.

These websites may use their own cookies, analytics, or data collection systems according to their respective privacy policies.

The application does not control or process any data collected by these external services.

4. Notifications

The app may send local notifications to remind users of available votes.

No personal information is used to schedule or send these notifications.

5. Security

Because no personal data is collected or transmitted, there is no risk of data exposure through the app.

6. Children’s Privacy

The app does not collect any personal data and may be safely used by users of all ages.

7. Changes

Any changes to this privacy policy will be updated on this page.

8. Contact

For any questions, please contact:

eldrazy.app@gmail.com
